com.google.appinventor.buildserver
Class Project

java.lang.Object
  com.google.appinventor.buildserver.Project

public final class Project
extends Object

This class gives access to Young Android project files.

A Young Android project file is essentially a Java properties file.

Author:
markf@google.com (Mark Friedman)
